title: Metagaming TFT Mega-Collection
description:
For over 5 years I have been collecting TFT and TFT-related materials until I had enough to fill a CD. I've finally done it! And here it is, even though I had to make some of the content myself ;)

In The Labyrinth
Advanced Melee
Advanced Wizard
Melee
Wizard
Death Test
Death Test 2
Grail Quest
Orb Quest
Security Station
Treasure of Unicorn Gold
Treasure of the Silver Dragon
The Forest Lords of Dihad
The Sorcerer's Manor
Starleader: Assault

Over 300 Megs of counters and paper minis

Maps and tiles galore, including a re-creation of the Roman Coliseum

Variants, house rules, expansions, clarifications aplenty

A new solitaire or team tile-based game system (created by me!)

Legends of the Ancient World
Legends of Time and Space
Legends of the Old West
Orcs of the High Mountains
Repel Boarders Starboard

And more!
